and
A20: p in { ( [#] X ) };
reconsider qx = q as (Point of X) by A19;
consider Q being (a_neighborhood of qx) such that A21: Q is  compact by A6,CKB11:def 1;
( [#] X ) c= ( [#] ( One-Point_Compactification X ) ) by CKB31:1;
