then (ex S being (Subset of X) st ((V = ( S \/ { ( [#] X ) } ) & S is  open) & ( S ` ) is  compact));
then ( [#] X ) in V by A36,XBOOLE_0:def 3;
then ( [#] X ) in ( [#] X ) by A40;
